Alert from '@zyxui/alert';
import { AlertCircleIcon, AlertTriangleIcon, CheckCircleIcon } from 'lucide-react';

<Alert
    title='Default Color (No Icon)'
    color='default'
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is a default color alert description! This example also shows that you can use alert without icon props.
        </span>
    }
/>
<hr className='my-4' />
<Alert
    title='Error Color (With Icon)'
    color='error'
    icon={<AlertCircleIcon />}
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is an error color alert description!
        </span>
    }
/>
<hr className='my-4' />
<Alert
    title='Warning Color'
    color='warning'
    icon={<AlertTriangleIcon />}
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is a warning color alert description!
        </span>
    }
/>
<hr className='my-4' />
<Alert
    title='Success Color'
    color='success'
    icon={<CheckCircleIcon />}
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is a success color alert description!
        </span>
    }
/>

import { AlertCircleIcon, AlertTriangleIcon, CheckCircleIcon } from 'lucide-react';

<Alert
    title='Default Color (No Icon)'
    color='default'
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is a default color alert description! This example also shows that you can use alert without icon props.
        </span>
    }
/>
<hr className='my-4' />
<Alert
    title='Error Color (With Icon)'
    color='error'
    icon={<AlertCircleIcon />}
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is an error color alert description!
        </span>
    }
/>
<hr className='my-4' />
<Alert
    title='Warning Color'
    color='warning'
    icon={<AlertTriangleIcon />}
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is a warning color alert description!
        </span>
    }
/>
<hr className='my-4' />
<Alert
    title='Success Color'
    color='success'
    icon={<CheckCircleIcon />}
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            This is a success color alert description!
        </span>
    }
/>

    variant='flat'

    radius='circle'

    }
/>

    title='none radius'
    variant='flat'
    radius='none'
    icon={<AlertTriangleIcon />}
    description={
        <span className='text-inherit'>
            None radius alert.
        </span>
    }
/>
